column5: hi guys! today was the day to put our canoe first time on water...bought last week from Canadien Tire in sale. me and my buddies Max and Ado went to wildwood today for some bass...good lake, bass were jumping and i got one largemouth and one smallmouth  ...that was it, nothing else for my buddie..shame , but that's it...we'll try next days

You gotta take your camera along next time Gino. We love fish porn here AT OFC. You should come across some pike at Wildwood as well. I haven't made my yearly trip there yet this year, soon maybe. Always had better luck with the smallies and pike than I did with largies at Wildwood.

btw ...how can i upload some pics...i tried uploading...i used "browse"...checked the file that i want to upload but it says "you did not select a file to upload"...hmmm....what could be the problem? thanks for help
I use a photo hosting site like myfishingpictures.com and just link the photo. Others use photobucket.
Dayum! Wildwood is in my backyard but I really need to get out there and explore.  JF
If you use the IMG Code link on the Photobucket the actuall picture will be posted instead of the link
